<H3>The usage of BEsTRF is comprehensively described in the <A HREF="BEsTRF_Manual.pdf">BEsTRF
manual</A> (currently for version 3.3, but new features are utilized easily without detailed instructions).</H3>

<H3>A <A HREF="BEsTRF_params.txt">comprehensive example</A> and a <A HREF="short_BEsTRF_params.txt">short summary</A> of parameters file are
also available, as well as a <A HREF="readme.txt">README file</A>.</H3>


